'''Akaliza Keza Gara ni''' umunyarwakazi w'umuhanga mu ikoranabuhanaga  n'itumanaho akaba n'umucuruzikazi <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/rwanda-today/akaliza-keza-gara-rwanda-s-ict-woman-1323180</ref>. Afite uruhare runini mu guteza imbere abakobwa kandi yamenyekanye kubera ibikorwa bye n'ibihembo byatanzwe na guverinoma y'u [[Rwanda]] ndetse n’umuryango mpuzamahanga w’itumanaho . '''Gara''' yashinze ubujyanama bwikoranabuhanga hamwe nisosiyete ikora urubuga hamwe na studio ya animasiyo. Yavuzweho kuba "umwe mu bagore bake bo mu [[Rwanda]] bateye intambwe igaragara mu guhindura isura y’ikoranabuhanga mu gihugu" kandi akaba umunyamuryango w’umuryango World Economic Forum’s Global Shapers Community<ref>http://www.techtalentfuture.com/akaliza-keza-gara-rwandan-it-activist-and-entrepreneur/</ref> <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/109151</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Akaliza Keza Gara yavukiye muri [[Uganda]] kandi yabayeho mu bihe bitandukanye muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]], [[Kenya]], [[Amerika]], [[Ubufaransa]], [[Ubusuwisi]], [[Ubutaliyani|n'Ubutaliyani]]. Afite impamyabumenyi ihanitse mu buhanga bwa multimediya no gushushanya yakuye muri kaminuza ya Kent, Canterbury (UK). <ref name="east" /> Yatuye i [[Kigali]], mu [[Rwanda]] nyuma yo kurangiza icyiciro cye maze atsindira akazi ke ka mbere mu 2009 akoresheje isoko ryo guhatanira urubuga rw’ubunyamabanga bwa Leta bwongerera ubushobozi abakozi ba Leta. Yari afite imyaka 23 y'amavuko kandi yagombaga kuguza mudasobwa igendanwa kugirango arangize akazi.  <ref name="klab">https://klab.rw/public/member/21</ref> Gara yashinze ubucuruzi bwa Multimedia Shaking Sun kugirango amwemere gutsindira imirimo myinshi mubijyanye no gushushanya, gukora imbuga na animasiyo no gutoza abana b'abanyarwanda. <ref name="east" /> Isosiyete yakoze imbuga za Minisiteri y’imari n’igenamigambi mu [[Rwanda]] na Minisiteri y’umutungo kamere. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/54835</ref>

Kuva muri Nzeri 2012, Gara yakoraga nk'umujyanama muri kLab, umuryango utanga ubufasha bw'ikoranabuhanga no gutanga inama ku bantu bo muri [[Kigali]] ndetse anakorana n'Abakobwa bo muri ICT Rwanda, umuryango uhuza abagore bakora mu bumenyi bw'ikoranabuhanga mu itumanaho kugira ngo bateze imbere ikoranabuhanaga nk'umwuga kubakobwa.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/54835</ref>   Ni umunyamuryango wa Kigali hub umuryango wa World Economic Forum’s Global Shapers Community. <ref name="venture">http://ventureburn.com/2014/04/built-in-africa-shaking-suns-akaliza-keza-gara-on-using-tech-to-tell-african-stories/</ref> Muri 2012 Gara yahawe igihembo cya Rwiyemezamirimo w’umugore witwaye neza muri ICT na Minisiteri y’Urubyiruko na ICT. <ref name="venture" /> Muri uwo mwaka, yari umwe mu bagore bane bo mu [[Rwanda]] ba rwiyemezamirimo ba ICT bamenyekanye nk'indashyikirwa mu nzego zabo n’umuryango mpuzamahanga w’itumanaho . <ref>http://www.ipsnews.net/2014/08/tech-entrepreneur-encourages-rwandas-young-women-to-venture-into-ict/</ref> Yatangiye gukoresha "Abanyarwanda kuri Twitter" (#RwOT) hashtag. <ref name="kig">https://web.archive.org/web/20180915053712/http://www.kigalian.com/socialmedia/2015/05/10-young-rwandan-entrepreneurs-you-should-follow-on-twitter/</ref>

Muri 2013, Microsoft yashyizeho Gara nk'uhagarariye urubyiruko muri Afurika y'Iburasirazuba, ku nshuro ya mbere Umunyarwanda ashyirwaho kuri uwo mwanya, kandi yari umwe mu bane bagize akanama ngishwanama k'urubyiruko muri gahunda ya 4Afrika.   <ref>http://www.kigalitoday.com/ikoranabuhanga/utuntu-n-utundi/Akariza-Keza-Gara-Umunyarwandakazi-watowe-mu-buyobozi-bwa-Microsoft-muri</ref>

Gara yashinze kandi Studiyo Yambi Animation. <ref name="kig" /> Arimo guteza imbere ''animasiyo ya African Tales'', izaba ikinamico ya mbere ya bana yakorewe mu [[Rwanda]].  Gara yakoze umushinga wa mbere wa cartoon mumwaka wa 2014, urukurikirane rwigisha abana, kandi yizera ko azateza imbere uwo mwuga hamwe nabana babanyaRwanda.<ref>http://www.ipsnews.net/2014/08/tech-entrepreneur-encourages-rwandas-young-women-to-venture-into-ict/</ref> 

Muri 2018, Gara yashyizweho n’umunyamabanga mukuru [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|w’umuryango w’abibumbye]] António Guterres kuba mu kanama gashinzwe ubufatanye bwa Digital<ref>https://blogs.kent.ac.uk/eda-news/2018/09/04/kent-alumna-from-rwanda-joins-high-level-un-panel-alongside-melinda-gates-and-jack-ma-and-makes-significant-strides-to-change-the-face-of-technology-in-her-country/</ref>. Muri ako kanama, Umunyamabanga mukuru yagize ati: “Ikoranabuhanga rya Digital rigira uruhare runini mu ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry’iterambere rirambye kandi bagabanya umwihariko ku mipaka mpuzamahanga. Ni yo mpamvu, ubufatanye mu bihugu byose ndetse no ku mipaka ari ingenzi kugira ngo hamenyekane ubushobozi bw’imibereho n’ubukungu by’ikoranabuhanga hifashishijwe ikoranabuhanga ndetse no kugabanya ingaruka ziterwa no kugabanya ingaruka zose zitateganijwe. ” <ref>https://www.un.org/press/en/2018/sga1817.doc.htm/</ref>

Gara yasobanuwe nk "umwe mu bagore bake bo mu [[Rwanda]] bateye intambwe igaragara mu guhindura isura y’ikoranabuhanga mu gihugu".  Yitabiriye Amahoro Binyuze mu Bucuruzi ndetse n'Ishuri Rikuru ry'Ubuyobozi mu masomo yo guhangana no gutera imbere ndetse muri 2017  yarangije icyiciro cya kabiri cya siyansi mu bumenyi bw'ikoranabuhanga yakuye muri Kobe Institute of Computing .  <ref>https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=waK8diEAAAAJ&hl=en</ref>

== Icyubahiro ==
Icyubahiro cyakiriwe na Akaliza Keza Gara kirimo:

* Impamyabumenyi y'icyubahiro yo muri kaminuza ya Kent
* Umwe mubagize akanama ngishwanama ka Microsoft 4Afrika
* Umwe mu bagize [[Umuryango w’Abibumye|akanama k’umuryango w’abibumbye]] ku bufatanye bwa Digital

